1935;;The Case of the Curious Bride;;American;;Michael Curtiz;;Warren William, Claire Dodd, Allen Jenkins;;drama, crime;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Case_of_the_Curious_Bride;;Rhoda Montaine learns that her first husband, Gregory Moxley, is still alive, which makes things awkward for her, since she has remarried Carl, the son of wealthy C. Phillip Montaine. She turns to Perry Mason for help, but when he goes to see Moxley, he finds only his corpse. Rhoda is arrested for murder.